{
  "stem": "7094.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] and she always remembers how pessimistic I was at that time, already realizing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When you look back, you realize how methodical, how systematic, how perfidious everything was done.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We didn't realize.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was a process continuous from '41 to '42 of dehumanizing you through hunger, through humiliation, fear, and ignorance.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were cut off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We didn't know what was happening in the next town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were not allowed to use the post.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were not allowed to travel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We didn't have any contact with the world outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were completely isolated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So a lot was ignorance, but a lot was methodical humiliation, you know, breaking up any spirit you had.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You know, when people talk to me, why did you go like lambs to the slaughter, it's very difficult to explain-- [PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] [DRINKS] --the process which was done.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I only see it now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I didn't see it then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECOND] 1st of May, 1942, I think it's a national holiday, a Socialist national [BACKGROUND NOISE] holiday in Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So we were all gathered together in the marketplace through the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We had all to come to the marketplace with everybody, ill, children, oldest, with everything-- we could just pack a packet.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a pronouncement that was--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pronouncement beforehand.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was told to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we all came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't know what was going to happen, but we all came because the police was going around.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what they have done on that particular-- I remember it was Sunday, a very sunny, beautiful day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "During the war, the '39, a building-- three buildings, [INAUDIBLE] cottages, were destroyed in one end of the town.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
